<br>
I'm not religious and my family no longer are either, despite spending the majority of my life being brought up in quite a religious(anglican) household. Nothing was ever forced upon me, and I was always encouraged to think things over...untill the a few years ago. I began to challenge more and more thing with people who used to 'teach' me, and so did mom. To cut a VERY long story short my parents are no longer religious, and I guess neither am I.<br>
<br>
