<br>
I believe in a higher power that resides within every living thing.  A step above the concept of the Transcendental Oversoul.  I strongly believe in reincarnation and the idea that souls live on.  I know they do, because I knew the exact second when my Grandma died, even though I wasn't there. I know when she visited me, and I knew when she decided to move on to the next life.  I'm just glad she stuck around for my wedding reception. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.bbarden.com/img/em/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
